{"tid":390197,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【央企重組】中建材及中材雙停牌 以待刊發內幕消息 (09:03)","createTime":"2017-09-07T01:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T03:45:17.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16db54b16e9c5b5180d4038277f9fbaf6273df05","tid":390197,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:43:07.000Z","msg":"文章日期：2017年9月7日<br />\n<br />\n中建材(3323)與中材(1893)今早開市前雙雙停牌，以待根據收購及合併守則刊發的一份內幕消息公告。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n中建材與中材母公司的合併重組方案已於今年首季完成，中材集團成為中建材集團的全資附屬公司。<br />\n<br />\n4.0x持有3323<br />\n我會唔會fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a063f973df55cb52e00feceadd91c81ce5313c0","tid":390197,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"中國中材股份有限公司下的中材國際(600970-CN)、寧夏建材(600449-CN)、祁連山(600720-CN)在上交所停牌，因重要事項待公告;北新建材(000786-CN)、天山股份(000877-CN)、中材科技(002080-CN)在深交所停牌，擬披露重大事項;中材股份(01893-HK)在香港停牌，等待刊發内幕消息。此外，華宇軟件(300271-CN)、友好集團(600778-CN)、迅遊科技(300467-CN)擬披露重大事項，證監會將審核三維通信(002115-CN)重大資産重組事項，9月7日開市起停牌。"},{"pid":"50817b3c76fd3b98bcafe4ec2102bf8fcd44059a","tid":390197,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"有冇清有貨？"},{"pid":"64bcee9d994b72135ee0a2d968127ebdb18d96ca","tid":390197,"uid":3738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇清有貨？</blockquote><br />\n1893 有一手3.55<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a676125a00220f0828cb10ed833cb14179346913","tid":390197,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"3323琴日想走走唔到<br />\n3.97貨<br />\n幾時先復牌先得架"},{"pid":"53d66cf9c6575819927a91c35ece8316f006693b","tid":390197,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3323琴日想走走唔到<br />\n3.97貨<br